92. How does the bubble sort algorithm work? What is its time complexity?
93. Explain the merge sort algorithm. What is its time complexity?
94. How does quicksort work? What is its average and worst-case time complexity?
95. What is the insertion sort algorithm, and what is its time complexity?
96. Explain the heap sort algorithm. What is its time complexity?
97. What is binary search? How does it work, and what is its time complexity?
98. How does linear search work? What is its time complexity?
99. What is the difference between merge sort and quicksort?
100. How do you perform binary search on a rotated sorted array?

